{"id": 475, "genre": 1001, "title": "你朋友圈出现过最奇怪的人是？", "description": "奥巴马请求加你为好友。", "record_count": 8845, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160606161857BtAKzXvdI5qig9H0.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-08-21T10:54:14Z", "options": [{"id": 9218, "content": "我。。。我吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 160555}, {"id": 8707, "content": "告诉你什么是真正的社会，教你什么是真正的兄弟，教你什么是真正的姐妹，教你怎么孝敬“咱爹吗”。现实中往往是loser", "image": null, "praise_count": 58, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 91804}, {"id": 8708, "content": "教你做人、讲义气、混社会的loser", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 91804}, {"id": 8709, "content": "你明明知道他她现实生活中是个什么样的人，却偏偏要看着他她在朋友圈装逼。", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 165209}, {"id": 8710, "content": "有一个阿姨天天转发女人不容易吧啦吧啦", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 98019}, {"id": 8711, "content": "一同事，下午看朋友圈推断她7点起床到下午2点平均一小时两条，当天晚上去ktv发了5个小视频，4条图片加文字，2条鸡汤…现在已经屏蔽", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 166592}, {"id": 8712, "content": "不管发什么动态，都会在最后配上一张看似毫无关联的、自、拍、照。", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 166593}, {"id": 8713, "content": "秀智商的下限，挑战我的底线。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 166641}, {"id": 12298, "content": "转，转，转", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 191513}, {"id": 8716, "content": "3天之内不转必有血光之灾之类的说说，下面还有+李易峰QQ:＆  呕心?", "image": null, "praise_count": 68, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 166679}, {"id": 8717, "content": "我自己，各种奇怪的想法，", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 166689}, {"id": 8718, "content": "发很短的一段文字，内容什么的明明什么都没表达清楚又好像什么都想说，装深沉。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 166694}, {"id": 8719, "content": "当裸照", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 166711}, {"id": 8720, "content": "傻不拉几抨击一些人\n然而并不懂他在干嘛", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 160641}, {"id": 8721, "content": "好好不说人话非要带点英语法语德语。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 160641}, {"id": 8722, "content": "照镜子一百遍都不厌倦，看别人总是瞟一眼。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 166721}, {"id": 8724, "content": "每天都说过眼云烟 一直没过完", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 6459}, {"id": 8725, "content": "自以为是的文艺。明明就是非主流。明明就是非主流。明明就是非主流！！！?", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 166799}, {"id": 8727, "content": "聚会发照片明显修图只修自己 不修朋友的=_=", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 166783}, {"id": 9239, "content": "变成微商还不准别人屏蔽", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 123244}, {"id": 8728, "content": "摇一摇摇到印度阿三", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 78476}, {"id": 8729, "content": "情侣晒恩爱，有意思吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 163785}, {"id": 8731, "content": "你发的每一天盆友圈都秒赞，开心的，闹心的，死了人的…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 166868}, {"id": 8732, "content": "装逼，各种秀，各种吃，各种闺蜜照，各种自拍照，各种点赞！最后，他们的生活和你没有任何关系，最后你就屏蔽他们了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 166369}, {"id": 9249, "content": "很喜欢盗别人的图 用别人的名字 别人的头像", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 169673}, {"id": 8738, "content": "每次都发一样的东西，而且每天都有，就想一个任务一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 166923}, {"id": 9508, "content": "天天刷自己的情路历程，明明她没和他在一起，他也讨厌她。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 170848}, {"id": 8741, "content": "看了大家写的意见 那么到底要在朋友圈发什么才算正常？", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 166990}, {"id": 8742, "content": "我有意见", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 167003}, {"id": 8744, "content": "一定要显示自己高大上的地理位置", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 167017}, {"id": 8748, "content": "在医院挂点滴先拍张照晒一晒，手腕被划到出血或脚踝肿成猪蹄也要先拍张照晒一晒…", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 166992}, {"id": 8750, "content": "晒娃", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 125127}, {"id": 8752, "content": "各种分享连接 小视频 好无聊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136181}, {"id": 8753, "content": "早段时间只有IOS才能发bug空白的内容 一条线刷屏...", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136181}, {"id": 8754, "content": "分享然并卵的内容 各种来自XX软件的分享", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136181}, {"id": 9010, "content": "明明啥都不知道，却装作百事通。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 168830}, {"id": 8755, "content": "私。信。求。点。赞。", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136181}, {"id": 8756, "content": "要么就一直死劲拍吃的遗照 要么就吃完拍个让人玩你猜我猜你今吃啥的图", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136181}, {"id": 8759, "content": "我就是那种微信和微博要同步的人，哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 152055}, {"id": 8760, "content": "一件很平常的事用不一样的叙事方式表达然后没人看的懂。好吧是我。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 167116}, {"id": 20280, "content": "长的这么胖也天天发朋友圈", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 269601}, {"id": 8761, "content": "秀不完的下限，没完没了的伤感！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 167120}, {"id": 9017, "content": "亲 第一条哦，赞一下，   给我孩子投票，第二个   亲做代理那？  炫富 停不下来。健身秀马甲线? 人鱼线?   磨N层的脸还往上晒！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 168852}, {"id": 9273, "content": "一个明明才22岁的外语系大学生，却成天愤世嫉俗地指责政治指点经济的早衰公知", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 160748}, {"id": 9529, "content": "每次打开都是他发的\n往下看还是\n在往下还是\n    ", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 170920}, {"id": 8762, "content": "各种微信小游戏 什么树洞表白 什么印象评论", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 81059}, {"id": 9274, "content": "一个因为成天跟对象矫情分了手，然后天天仍旧各种矫情的……找不到合适的形容词", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 160748}, {"id": 9275, "content": "逢谣言必传从不动脑子琢磨的二傻子——而且这人有个毛病，看见朋友圈里有什么都点赞", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 160748}, {"id": 8764, "content": "这里面的人相互看看就能撕起来别说朋友圈了", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164474}, {"id": 8766, "content": "好的产品设计是什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 167138}]}